Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Global climate change
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8hc3
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 May 1975
Forecasters claim global weather is cooling. Folk memory disagrees. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.